API Catalogs

Source: R/catalogs.R
catalogs.Rd

List of API catalogs:

  • care: CMS Medicare API

  • prov: CMS Provider API

  • open: CMS Open Payments API

  • caid: CMS Medicaid API

  • hgov: CMS HealthCare.gov API

Usage

catalogs()

Value

<list> of catalogs

Examples

catalogs()
